<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />春天來了，<delay8 />天氣變得暖和多了啊。<delay frames="40" />
那我來練習個<tag a="135" b="6" arg="0xcd00" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />鬆一鬆凍僵的筋骨好了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay20 />現在我得先想辦法<delay8 />
抵擋這股濃濃睡意才行<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Sleepy" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />呼啊～<delay frames="40" /><tag a="110" b="5" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hot" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呼～<delay20 />好熱喔！<delay frames="40" />
我都熱到滿身大汗了！<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過一想到<delay20 />這是在考驗我的幹勁，<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />鬥志好像就燃燒起來啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有好好享受<delay20 />這個秋天嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是呆呆地坐著，<delay8 />秋天可是轉眼就過囉！<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />秋天啊，<delay20 />真的是個很棒的季節耶！<delay frames="40" />
不只氣溫非常適合做運動，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />更重要的是，<delay8 />食物也很好吃！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ColdChill" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗚～<delay20 />好冷好冷！<delay frames="30" />
冬天真的到了呢……<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說到冬天，我想到我小時候有個夢想，<delay20 />
就是做一個超級大的雪洞，<delay8 />
然後住進去呢～<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我說<tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay20 />
下次我們一起試試看吧？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />咦？<delay frames="40" /><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒有啦，<delay20 />我沒有叫你跟我一起住喔！</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我總覺得花朵<delay20 />
看起來好像很開心耶。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是不是因為春天來了啊？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說起來，<delay8 />我以前還住在老家的時候，<delay20 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在附近山上<delay8 />抓了幾十隻蟬，<delay8 />
結果拿回家炫耀給老媽看以後……<pageBreak /><10_10 /><tag a="10" b="12" /><size value="150" /><anim id="Outraged" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay8 />給我帶回去放生！！<size value="100" /><pageBreak /><10_9 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />她露出超嚇人的表情，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />生氣地對著我大吼啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />白天的時間越來越短了呢，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我才稍微發個呆，<delay8 />
天色就馬上暗下來了。<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你知道這種季節變化<delay8 />要怎麼形容嗎？<10_4 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那就是<delay20 />「秋天的太陽落得快」喔！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦？<delay20 />沒有人這樣說嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這麼冷的天氣，<delay8 />火鍋吃起來更美味呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />話說回來，我在好幾年前<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />請朋友吃了<delay8 />
<tag a="110" b="10" />特製火鍋呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不曉得是不是<delay8 />因為太感動了，<delay20 />
那傢伙還幫我的火鍋取了一個<10_4 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />叫「黑暗火鍋」<delay20 />的名字喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="10" arg="0x65 0x65 0x65 0x65 0x66 0x66" /></message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="10" arg="0x67 0x67 0x67 0x67 0x67 0x68" /></message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="0" arg="0x69 0x6a" /></message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="8" arg="0x6b 0x6b 0x6c 0x6c 0x6c 0x6c 0x6b" /></message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />天氣完全回暖了耶！<delay frames="40" />
植物和昆蟲們也都從地下冒出來……<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總覺得<delay8 />我也跟著雀躍起來了！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果看到牠們的話，<delay8 />我有點忍不住想喊聲<delay20 />
「早安！」試試呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />什、<delay20 />什麼啦？<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你那驚訝的表情<delay8 />是什麼意思啊！？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這個季節<delay8 />一到晚上，<delay20 />
就會突然變得很冷，<delay8 />你要多注意喔！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果因為白天很溫暖而大意<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><tag a="10" b="12" /><anim id="Sneezing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><10_10 /><delay frames="16" /><size value="150" />哈～啾！！<size value="100" /><delay20 /><10_9 /><pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就會像這樣！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也要小心，<delay20 />
別讓自己<delay8 />感冒了喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />夏天的時候啊，<delay20 />一直喊好熱好熱，<delay frames="30" />
你不覺得反而會變得更熱嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />既然這樣，<delay20 />那說好冷的話，<delay20 />
是不是就會覺得比較涼爽了？<delay frames="30" />
<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />唉，<delay20 />應該不可能吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hot" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就算太陽下山了，也還是好熱喔。<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />晚上睡不著的話，<delay8 />就只好熬夜了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過就算到了晚上，<delay8 />
天氣也還是這麼熱<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這裡該不會<delay8 />就是傳說中的熱島吧！？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay20 />
說到秋天你會想到什麼啊？<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想到的是運動之秋！<pageBreak /><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />運動完以後，飯吃起來特別美味呢！<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不對，<delay frames="30" /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣好像變成<delay8 />食慾之秋了？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay20 />
說到秋天，你會想到什麼啊？<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />應該會是<delay8 />藝術之秋吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯～<delay8 />畢竟看了以水果為主題的畫，<delay20 />
肚子都會忍不住叫出聲嘛～<delay frames="50" />
不對，<delay frames="30" /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣好像變成<delay8 />食慾之秋了？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這個季節的空氣特別冷，<delay20 />
臉總是<delay8 />動不動就覺得痛呢。<pageBreak />和別人打架以後<delay8 />吹到風的話，<delay20 />
那可是會比平常還要痛上個好幾倍啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay frames="30" /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿，<delay20 />這都是以前的事了啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="108" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一看到下雪，<delay8 />我就會跟著興奮起來，<delay20 />
甚至會忘了外面天寒地凍呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />以前住在老家的時候，<delay20 />我也常和死黨一起<delay8 />
在雪中玩得不亦樂乎喔～<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯，<delay20 />進行那麼劇烈的運動，<delay8 />自然不覺得冷啊？</message>
</msbt>